values: It all begins when you start feeling lonely. You start to pity yourself and ask God to give you someone to be with. Then after some time you try to get close to any girl you meet, but it doesn't work out. You pity yourself. And you always fail. After some time and some more fails you start to take pleasure in it. You pity yourself and take pleasure. Then finally you find someone who wants to be with you. You are calm for a while. Then it starts to bore you. And you fail again. She leaves. You pity yourself and take pleasure in it, though you curse your life and destiny. Some time passes. You realize that you've made a mistake, that you've missed your chance to be happy. You pity yourself and take pleasure in it. You think that it is a God's plan for you. Some kind of divine destiny, and that you were created for some bigger purpose, other than being with someone. And then you die... And nothing comes out of it. Everything comes to an end.
